body:
What are your thoughts on the following Ezreal build?

The 40% CDR from Iceborn Gauntlets and Black Cleaver gives me a 2.7 sec cooldown on Q, nice armour shred, utility, slow, life steal and a huge mana pool. 

{{item:3006}} {{item:3042}} {{item:3025}} {{item:3153}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3072}}

replies.body:
You mean this build:
{{item:3078}} {{item:3022}} {{item:3031}} {{item:3508}}  {{item:3033}} {{item:3006}} 
I feel with his current state and the high natural attack speed this is probably the build to go with, offering him strong damage and cdr allowing him to take more traditional adc runes. This build burns mana fast but he does so much damage and he kites even better than his blue build like this.

His ap build is kinda fun in midlane too, taking the classic midlane mage runes: ap quints, magic pen reds, scaling hp yellows, 3 flat magic resist and 6 scaling cdr blues:
{{item:3100}} {{item:3116}} {{item:3285}} {{item:3115}} {{item:3135}} {{item:3020}}
